Q.  Why in particular though?  I mean, obviously you won, but what especially?
 
DARIO FRANCHITTI:  Toronto, I guess is the fact that, you know, we won in such a controlled manner.  And Australia pretty much the same.  I think the pole position in Australia really gave me a great deal of satisfaction. 
 
Q.  Right.
 
DARIO FRANCHITTI:  To be, I guess whatever point lead I had or whatever. I mean that really, you know, I was really happy with that one. 
 
