DARIO FRANCHITTI:  Who knows.  I mean, I have a contract next year with team KOOL green.  And after that, anything is possible.  
 
Q.  And Juan? 
 
JUAN MONTOYA:  I don't know, you know.  I gotta deal with Chip next year as well.  You know, you never know what happens.  
 
